metadata.name: The Amazing Fitz Roy
metadata.description:
The most incredible sunset of my life, a sunset that makes you cry with emotion, it's not just a photo, it's moments that stay forever in our memory, it felt like there was something on fire behind this beautiful mountain, it was one of the most incredible days of my life, and I'm glad I managed to keep all that emotion in this photo.
